---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Cookie Policy | ItalianVenues" 
  description="Learn about how we use cookies and similar technologies on our website."
>
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="relative bg-black py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-900 to-black opacity-90"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <p class="text-[#a78656] text-sm md:text-base font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">Legal Information</p>
      <h1 class="heading-h1 text-white mb-6">
        Cookie Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-base md:text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' })}
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cookie Policy Content -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile) when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide information to website owners.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed">
            This Cookie Policy explains how ItalianVenues ("we", "our", "us") uses cookies and similar technologies on our website at <a href="https://italianvenues.com" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline">italianvenues.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Types of Cookies -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-3 mt-6">2.1 Strictly Necessary Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            These cookies are essential for the website to function properly. They enable core functionality such as security, network management, and accessibility.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 mb-6">
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mb-2"><strong>Examples:</strong></p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Session management</li>
              <li>Security and authentication</li>
              <li>Load balancing</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mt-3"><strong>Duration:</strong> Session or up to 1 year</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm"><strong>Can be disabled:</strong> No (required for site to work)</p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-3 mt-6">2.2 Performance and Analytics Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website by collecting and reporting information anonymously. This helps us improve the website's performance and user experience.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 mb-6">
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mb-2"><strong>Examples:</strong></p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Google Analytics (if implemented)</li>
              <li>Page visit tracking</li>
              <li>User behavior analysis</li>
              <li>Error reporting</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mt-3"><strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 2 years</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm"><strong>Can be disabled:</strong> Yes (via browser settings)</p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-3 mt-6">2.3 Functionality Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            These cookies allow the website to remember choices you make (such as language preferences) and provide enhanced, more personalized features.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 mb-6">
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mb-2"><strong>Examples:</strong></p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Remembering your preferences</li>
              <li>Language selection</li>
              <li>Saved search filters</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mt-3"><strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 1 year</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm"><strong>Can be disabled:</strong> Yes (via browser settings)</p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-3 mt-6">2.4 Targeting/Advertising Cookies</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            These cookies may be set through our site by our advertising partners. They may be used to build a profile of your interests and show you relevant advertisements on other sites.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 mb-6">
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mb-2"><strong>Examples:</strong></p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Facebook Pixel (if implemented)</li>
              <li>Google Ads remarketing (if implemented)</li>
              <li>Social media tracking pixels</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm mt-3"><strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 2 years</p>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 text-sm"><strong>Can be disabled:</strong> Yes (via browser settings or opt-out links)</p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Third-Party Cookies -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We may use third-party service providers who set cookies on our website to provide their services. These may include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website analytics and performance monitoring</li>
            <li><strong>Social Media Platforms:</strong> For social sharing functionality (Facebook, Instagram, Pinterest)</li>
            <li><strong>Content Delivery Networks:</strong> For faster loading of images and resources</li>
            <li><strong>Hosting Providers:</strong> Vercel for website hosting and delivery</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            These third parties have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- How to Control Cookies -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">4. How to Control and Delete Cookies</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-3 mt-6">4.1 Browser Settings</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Most web browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. You can usually find these settings in the "Options" or "Preferences" menu of your browser. Here are links to cookie settings for popular browsers:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Google Chrome</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/cookies-information-websites-store-on-your-computer" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-sfri11471/mac" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Safari (macOS)</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/en-gb/HT201265" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Safari (iOS)</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/delete-cookies-in-microsoft-edge-63947406-40ac-c3b8-57b9-2a946a29ae09" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-3 mt-6">4.2 Opt-Out Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            You can also use these tools to opt out of targeted advertising:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 space-y-2">
            <li><a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.com/" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Your Online Choices (EU)</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://optout.networkadvertising.org/" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Network Advertising Initiative (US)</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">Digital Advertising Alliance (US)</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-3 mt-6">4.3 Mobile Device Settings</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed">
            On mobile devices, you can usually control tracking through your device settings:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li><strong>iOS:</strong> Settings → Privacy → Tracking → Disable "Allow Apps to Request to Track"</li>
            <li><strong>Android:</strong> Settings → Google → Ads → Opt out of Ads Personalization</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Impact of Disabling Cookies -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">5. What Happens if You Disable Cookies?</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you choose to disable cookies, some features of our website may not function properly. For example:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Your preferences may not be saved</li>
            <li>Some pages may load more slowly</li>
            <li>You may not be able to use certain interactive features</li>
            <li>We may not be able to provide personalized recommendations</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            However, you will still be able to browse the website and submit enquiries.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Local Storage -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">6. Other Technologies</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            In addition to cookies, we may use other technologies to store information:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> To save your search preferences and filters locally in your browser</li>
            <li><strong>Session Storage:</strong> To maintain state during your browsing session</li>
            <li><strong>Web Beacons/Pixels:</strong> Small graphics that help us track page visits and email opens</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Updates to Policy -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">7. Updates to This Cookie Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable laws. We encourage you to review this policy periodically. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates when this policy was last revised.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">8. Questions About Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you have any questions about our use of cookies or this Cookie Policy, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-zinc-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200">
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@italianvenues.com" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline">privacy@italianvenues.com</a></p>
            <p class="text-zinc-700 mb-2"><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> <a href="https://wa.me/447728331698" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline" target="_blank">+44 7728 331698</a></p>
            <p class="text-zinc-700"><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="/contact" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline">Contact Form</a></p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Related Policies -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif text-zinc-900 mb-4">9. Related Policies</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            For more information about how we handle your data, please see:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-zinc-700 space-y-2">
            <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/terms" class="text-[#a78656] hover:underline">Terms & Conditions</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

